 CHIOMA GABRIEL The birth of a child is almost always a cause for celebration. Although the good book says that the faithful would deliver like 'Hebrew women', what many don't know is that childbirth is sometimes dangerous for women. Nigeria records one of the world's highest rates of maternal… November 22, 2014 In "Special Report" The Economic and Financial Crimes Commission, EFCC, has arraigned a former Minister of Works and Housing, Dr. Hassan Lawal on a 9 count fresh criminal charge bordering on money laundering and embezzlement of N44 million. May 17, 2011 In "News" After the Pastor had handed back the baby to its parents at this baby dedication at a Church, the mother said she had a testimony linked to its birth. She was given the microphone. June 23, 2013 In "Vista Woman"